  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "两个整数的最大公约数，是能同时整除它们的最大正整数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "比如四十八和三十六，它们的最大公约数是十二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "两千多年前，欧几里得给出了一个惊人简洁的求法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "divide-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/divide-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "用大数除以小数，取余数，再用小数除以这个余数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "divide-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/divide-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "如此辗转反复，直到余数变成零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "divide-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/divide-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "最后那个非零的除数，就是最大公约数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-1",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/geometry-geo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "把两数看成矩形的长和宽，不断从中切下最大的正方形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-2",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/geometry-geo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "剩下的小矩形继续切，正方形越切越小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-3",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/geometry-geo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "最后一块正方形的边长，正是最大公约数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "extend",
      "line_id": "ext-1",
      "filename": "extend-ext-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/extend-ext-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "扩展算法不仅求出公约数，还能找到两个系数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "extend",
      "line_id": "ext-2",
      "filename": "extend-ext-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/extend-ext-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "a 乘以 x 加上 b 乘以 y，恰好等于它们的公约数，这就是裴蜀等式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "选择不同的两个数，看看辗转相除每一步的算式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "观察矩形是怎样被一层层正方形填满的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "辗转相除用余数一步步逼近，是最古老的高效算法之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "它的几何形态是矩形切正方形，代数延伸是裴蜀等式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "euclidean-algorithm",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/euclidean-algorithm/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "简单的取余，藏着深刻的数学，我们下次再见！"
    }
